# 🚀 Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Brain-Disease-Classification-EEG.git
```

Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Download the OpenNeuro dataset and update the dataset path in the source code.

---

# ▶️ Running

```bash
python final.py
```

Generated visualizations are saved inside the `outputs/` directory.

